      "sub2": "List b — all b values produced for a2. May be empty.",
      "sub3": "List b — all b values produced for a3. May be empty.",
      "flatten": "Concatenate: sub1 ++ sub2 ++ sub3. This is the key step: all branches merged into one flat List b.",
      "lb": "List b — the complete output: sub1 ++ sub2 ++ sub3. Non-determinism is preserved as multiple values."
    },
    "title": "List bind (concatMap): apply f to every element, concatenate all results — also called: flatMap, SelectMany, List.collect, >>=",
